@Comment:	Rick reports that in conversation prior to recording , Eve was trying to find something. Mother said , "I don't know..." Rick said , "I don't know." Eve probably heard "I don't know..." several times , but no other form of the negative was used. Then Eve said , "I don't know... I do not know."
